snippet: Fiercely debated ammunition limits cleared the state’s Democratic-led legislature on Wednesday and were on their way to Gov. John W. Hickenlooper, who has said he will sign them.
abstract: Fiercely debated ammunition limits clear Colorado's Democratic-led legislature and go to Gov John W Hickenlooper, who has said he will sign them.
lead_paragraph: Fiercely debated ammunition limits cleared the state’s Democratic-led legislature on Wednesday and were on their way to Gov. John W. Hickenlooper, who has said he will sign them.
